></a><a href="/whv/𣀹"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x23039;</span></a><a href="/whv/𣀶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x23036;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢑊"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2244A;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡿍"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x21FCD;</span></a><a href="/whv/鑽"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x947D;</span></a><a href="/whv/酇"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x9147;</span></a><a href="/whv/躦"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8EA6;</span></a><a href="/whv/讚"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8B9A;</span></a><a href="/whv/襸"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8978;</span></a><a href="/whv/臢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x81E2;</span></a><a href="/whv/纘"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7E98;</span></a><a href="/whv/籫"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7C6B;</span></a><a href="/whv/穳"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7A73;</span></a><a href="/whv/禶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x79B6;</span></a><a href="/whv/礸"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7938;</span></a><a href="/whv/瓚"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x74DA;</span></a><a href="/whv/灒"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7052;</span></a><a href="/whv/欑"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6B11;</span></a><a href="/whv/攢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6522;</span></a><a href="/whv/巑"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5DD1;</span></a><a href="/whv/囋"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x56CB;</span></a><a href="/whv/劗"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5297;</span></a><a href="/whv/儹"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5139;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Ho%E1%BA%A1-tham-t%C3%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BA%A7n-h%C3%A0nh-dinh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-c%C3%BAc-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-h%E1%BB%B1u-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-kkpiLPKmtSBVmDSxOrnpaA">Hoạ tham tán đại thần hành dinh thưởng cúc thập vịnh hựu phú thập vịnh kỳ 01 - 和參贊大臣行營賞菊十詠又賦十詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/Khai-Nghi%C3%AAm-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-Ug6pP1nw6eIAs6JFO-TjWg">Khai Nghiêm tự bi ký - 開嚴寺碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/L%C6%B0u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-An-L%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-6as8evR1Y29imQV8m_rmzA">Lưu đề An Lạc tự kỳ 3 - 留題安樂寺其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Man-ph%E1%BB%A5-h%C3%A0nh/poem-KJN5tsLol60-b4VrQaFSQw">Man phụ hành - 蠻婦行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/M%E1%BA%B7c/poem-T8HqXV-PoyItvBaUpM_rrA">Mặc - 墨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/S%E1%BA%AFc-t%E1%BB%A9-T%C3%BA-Phong-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-xxLxY7z4rcP4cV-gZh2gaw">Sắc tứ Tú Phong tự bi - 敕賜秀峰寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%A1-Hoa-ch%E1%BB%89-huy-t%E1%BB%91ng-th%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-th%C3%B4ng-t%C3%ADch/poem-eTpzLDCWOaabTOhJgkFNvg">Tạ Hoa chỉ huy tống thú đầu thông tích - 謝花指揮送獸頭通脊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%E1%BB%A5c-ph%C3%A1n-quan-s%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%A2y-phi%C3%AAn/poem-Eln7UzT_jIi6xc1ZwNyliA">Tống Dương lục phán quan sứ tây phiên - 送楊六判官使西蕃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A3o-H%E1%BA%A3o-thi/poem-ZLgiAlRmZdlWf7MkDKd1sg">Trương Hảo Hảo thi - 張好好詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/T%E1%BB%AB-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-minh-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-CmcW-aGSq0U6WnbHUzXRPg">Từ Ân tự bi minh tịnh tự - 慈恩寺碑銘并序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
